Shaun Dingwall https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shaun_Dingwall 0 Shaun Dingwall (born 24 March 1972) is an English actor. He is best known for his roles as Pete Tyler in Doctor Who, as Reg Trotter in Rock and Chips and as D.C. Mark Rivers in Touching Evil. Shaun_Dingwall ( born 24_March_1972 ) is an_English_actor .
